# Static public assets.
#
# Voice interview is push-to-talk only — no client-side VAD.
# The previous Silero ONNX integration (@ricky0123/vad-web) was
# removed: 13 MB of wasm + an onnxruntime-web dep-optimizer skirmish
# with Vite, replaced by an AudioWorklet-only PCM capture pipeline
# in src/features/interview/voice/AudioCapture.ts.
#
# Server-side VAD on Paraformer is also disabled — the STT client is
# constructed with use_server_vad=False in
# merism/voice/setup.py. Turn boundaries are explicit: PTT press
# → talk → PTT release.
